    "[7] investigated crowdsourced photos for damage assessment.",
    "Multimodal Fusion Techniques: Recent multimodal disaster research has achieved significant breakthroughs through sophisticated fusion strategies.",
    "El-Niss et al. [8] looked into federated learning approaches with F1-score 85.2%, and Khattar et al.",
